NG0756:2: maha ka la shri trai d+ha du b+hai ra wa na ma tan tra /
NG0756:4: dpal nag po chen po khams gsum 'jigs byed kyi rgyud ces bya ba /
NG0756:5: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0756:6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
NG0756:7: ston pa'i mchog bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs
NG0756:8: pa'i sangs rgyas dpal mchog rdo rje 'chang chen gnas
NG0756:9: kyi mchog dur khrod na bzhugs /
NG0756:10: 'khor mchog sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen po rnams dang */
NG0756:11: byang chub sems mchog bsrung mdzad pa //
NG0756:12: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro ma la sogs pa yi //
NG0756:13: skal ldan skyes bu rnams dang thabs cig go / de tshe ston mchog bcom ldan 'das nyid kyis //
NG0756:14: sangs rgyas bstan pa la gnod cing de spyod pa'i //
NG0756:15: dge 'dun dkon la 'tshe mang don ched du //
NG0756:16: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung thabs rgyud mchog gsungs //
NG0756:17: mos mchog sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung 'dod pas //
NG0756:18: log dad sel sogs rgyal ba bsam yas kyis //
NG0756:19: dbang bskur bstan pa bsrung bar rjes gnang ba'i //
NG0756:20: gdul dka' 'dul mchog nag chen dpal bsgrub bya //
NG0756:21: bstan pa'i don bsdus sdig spang dge sgrub yin //
NG0756:22: de bas nyon mongs dbang gis gsad pa'i las //
NG0756:23: sbyor byed bstan pa'i don dang 'gal bas na //
NG0756:24: sdig 'gyur drag pas bstan bsrungs ma yin te //
NG0756:25: byams dang snying rje dge bas bdud bsgral phyir //
NG0756:26: rgyal ba'i bka' bzhin drag po'i las byas na //
NG0756:27: sdig can gnas spor dge 'gyur nyes pa med //
NG0756:28: sems dge bkar bzhin byas na bsgral phyir dge ba yin //
NG0756:29: mdo rgyud kun las gsungs pa'i don //
NG0756:30: kun rdzob dang ni don dam bden par bstan //
NG0756:32: kun rdzob ma rig rtog pas brtags pa ste //
NG0756:33: snang ba rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yin //
NG0756:35: kun rdzob chos nyid don dam stong nyid de //
NG0756:36: dngos po ci yang grub pa med pa yin //
NG0756:37: dngos po med nyid 'khrul la dngos por snang *//
NG0756:38: dngos snang nyid la snang la dngos med kyang *//
NG0756:40: stong nyid rtogs pa gom mthar ma phyin par //
NG0756:41: kun rdzob dge sdig rgyu dang 'bras bu rnams //
NG0756:42: med min sdug bsngal rgyur gyur sdig pa yang *//
NG0756:43: bde ba'i rgyu mthun dge la 'jug bya ste //
NG0756:45: dge la 'jug tshul sna tshogs thabs gsungs kyang *//
NG0756:46: thabs chen spyod pa gsang sngags theg pa'i mchog / thabs mchog shes rab dam pa zung 'jug lam //
NG0756:47: thabs mang bsgrub sla myur 'grub 'di ltar bslab //
NG0756:48: dam tshig dbang bskur thob byas ma nyams pas //
NG0756:49: lta spyod mthun pa'i grogs bzang da 'grogs shing *//
NG0756:50: dben zhing nyams dga' dben pa'i gnas btsal la //
NG0756:51: gang dgos yo byad bsgrub sla nyer bsdogs nas //
NG0756:52: man+dal chos rdzas la sogs legs par bsham //
NG0756:53: dpal ldan mgon nag chen po bsgrub pa yi //
NG0756:55: gzhan dge sbyor sna tshogs pa'i //
NG0756:56: bya ba mang po spangs la mchog 'od sgrub //
NG0756:57: drin can mchog gsum dkon mchog gsum rnams la //
NG0756:58: khyad par can gyi skyabs 'gro lan mang bya //
NG0756:59: dang po gsum dmigs byang chub mchog sems bskyed //
NG0756:60: rgyu mthun sa bon yongs 'gyur thugs mtshan las //
NG0756:61: bsnyen byed sngags brjod lha sku bskyed //
NG0756:62: lus ngag yid la sku gsung thugs byin brlab //
NG0756:63: mthu ldan sngags kyis bgegs bskrad gnas bsrung zhing *//
NG0756:64: dgos pa'i rdzas gsum khyad par 'phags par bya //
NG0756:65: byang chub mchog tu sems skyed cho ga bdun //
NG0756:66: sbyong phyir tshad med bzhi dang bcas pa yis //
NG0756:67: kun rdzob rgya chen byang chub sems bskyed pas //
NG0756:68: bsod nams tshogs bsogs don dam sems skye'i rgyud //
NG0756:69: bsod nams tshogs sngon song nas ye shes tshogs //
NG0756:70: bsag thabs don dam zab mo byang chub mchog / sems ni bsgom bskyed de las gzhan gyis min //
NG0756:71: don dam par na chos kyi chos nyid ni //
NG0756:72: ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa nyid yin te //
NG0756:73: 'khrul pas dngos med nyid de dngos brtags snang *//
NG0756:74: snang tshe dngos med sor sor rtogs pa yis //
NG0756:75: shes rab kyis rtogs bya de mnyam par gzhag /
NG0756:76: om shu n+ya ta dz+nya na badzra swa b+ha wa
NG0756:77: at+ma ko\u0f85ham / zhes pa'i sngags kyis don bsgom /
NG0756:78: de ltar bsod nams tshogs dang ye shes tshogs //
NG0756:79: mdo rgyud phyi nang thun mong mngon byas nas //
NG0756:80: de nas thun mong ma yin lam gyi mchog / gsang sngags bskyed dang rdzogs rim bsgom bya ste //
NG0756:81: gang gis stong nyid sgom pa'i ngang nyid las //
NG0756:82: snang ba rten cing 'brel pa 'byung tshul ni //
NG0756:83: rang sems pam yig pad+ma 'dab brgyad pa //
NG0756:84: lte bar ram skyes tshe 'gyur bsam steng du //
NG0756:85: hum yig mthing nag 'od zer 'bar ba bsgom //
NG0756:86: de las 'od 'phros sna tshogs rdo rje bsam //
NG0756:87: de dag 'od 'phros rdo rje sa gzhi dang *//
NG0756:88: ra ba gur dang me lce 'bar ba bskyed //
NG0756:89: de nas b+h+rumm las gzhal yas khang legs pa //
NG0756:90: lha yi gdan dang bcas pa bskyed par bya //
NG0756:92: rgyal mchod sems can sgrib sbyangs mgon por gyur //
NG0756:94: 'od zer mgon po'i phyag mtshan kun bsdus te //
NG0756:95: tha la thim 'gyur ral gri tha mtshan bsam //
NG0756:96: tha ya ra na phat ces sngags brjod do //
NG0756:99: mgon po'i skur gyur ma lus kun 'dus nas //
NG0756:100: 'og min gnas su rnam snang sku la thim //
NG0756:101: de yi thugs nas tha de mdun du 'byung *//
NG0756:102: sam ta ra ni hum zhes gsang sngags brjod //
NG0756:103: de'i rjes rang mthun tha de las //
NG0756:104: dpal 'bar mgon nag chen po khro bo'i sku //
NG0756:105: bdud bzhi'i dgra dpung 'dzems pa yi //
NG0756:106: dpa' bo chen po khams gsum 'jigs byed pa //
NG0756:107: zhal gcig phyag bzhi zhabs gnyis sku chen mchog / gzi brjid bskal pa'i me ltar rab tu 'bar //
NG0756:110: sku dang zhal ni char sprin mthing nag mdog / phyag na glang po'i rgyal mtshan ral gri dang *//
NG0756:111: dbyug pa dang ni zhags pa'i phyag char ldan //
NG0756:112: khro gnyer gnyer zhing smin ma glog ltar 'khyug /
NG0756:113: mche ba gtsigs shing zhal du khrag 'thung 'dzag /
NG0756:114: sma ra dbu skra kham nag gyen du 'khyil //
NG0756:115: rin chen mgo skam spel mas skra tshar brgyan //
NG0756:116: rgyal ba rigs lnga dbu rgyan tshul du bzhugs //
NG0756:117: mi mgo brgya phyed 'phreng bas do shal byas //
NG0756:118: mgul do dpung rgyan rin chen mdzes ba mnga' //
NG0756:119: klu chen brgyad ni sbrul gzugs sku la brgyan //
NG0756:120: ye shes me dpung 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NG0756:121: pad+ma 'od mchog steng du sprul pa'i sku //
NG0756:122: lha yi gtso brgyad zhabs gnyis kyis mnan te //
NG0756:123: bzhengs nas gong zhing bsdigs pa'i tshul du bzhugs //
NG0756:124: de ltar dam tshig mgon nag cher gsal bsgom //
NG0756:126: de yi thugs khar ye shes sems dpa' bsam //
NG0756:127: ye shes sems dpa'i snying na ting nge 'dzin //
NG0756:128: sems dpa' gsal dmigs de las 'khor bskyed pa //
NG0756:129: gcer bu pa dang ye shes ma mo bdun //
NG0756:130: rgyal chen bzhi dang klu rigs lcam dral lo //
NG0756:131: legs ldan nag chen gcer bu pa //
NG0756:132: zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'jigs byed gzugs //
NG0756:133: kha t+wam kha dang be con thogs //
NG0756:134: khro bo rgyan ldan ro stong bzhugs //
NG0756:135: ye shes ma mo kang ka bdun pa ni //
NG0756:136: nag mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis gri thod thogs //
NG0756:137: yi dwags gdan bzhugs khro bo rgyan cha can //
NG0756:139: 'khor gyi gtso chen brgyad po de la yang *//
NG0756:140: nag po che dang ma mo'i tshogs //
NG0756:142: 'bum phrag bzhi bcu rtsa dgus bskor //
NG0756:143: gtso 'khor dgu yi lus ngag yid de nyid //
NG0756:144: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlab //
NG0756:145: de nas ye shes mgon nag chen po nyid //
NG0756:146: 'khor bcas spyan drangs byas te rkang dung 'bud //
NG0756:147: mda' dar nag po g.yab cing sman khrag phyar //
NG0756:148: gal te 'khor bcas spyan 'dren tshig la ni //
NG0756:150: sngar gyi sngags mi brjod par skad ni 'di skad brjod //
NG0756:151: mgon po chen po'i bka' nyan gsung sdod ni //
NG0756:152: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NG0756:153: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i bdag po ni //
NG0756:154: legs ldan nag po chen po chos skyong gtso //
NG0756:155: lha yi dmag dpon chen po gshegs su gsol //
NG0756:156: kang ka mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas te gshegs //
NG0756:157: klu dang rgyal chen lcam dral ma lus pa //
NG0756:158: dam chos skyong ba'i bsrung ma thams cad dang *//
NG0756:159: lha yi dmag dang bcas pa gshegs su gsol //
NG0756:160: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NG0756:161: bdag cag sgrub pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NG0756:162: e h+ye dz+nya na maha ka la sa pa ri wa ra sa dz+nya dza sa ma dza /
NG0756:163: chos rnams chos nyid gdod nas gnyis med cas //
NG0756:164: bdag dang lha yang gnyis su med mod kyang *//
NG0756:167: de las sdug bsngal rang bzhin 'khor 'gyur phyir //
NG0756:168: rtog 'dul gnyen por dam tshig ye shes lha //
NG0756:169: gnyis med yin te yin par go bya'i phyir //
NG0756:170: dam tshig lha la ye shes lha yi sku //
NG0756:171: gnyis 'dres tshul du thim zhing bzhugs su gsol //
NG0756:172: sa ma ya dz+nya na de ba sa ma tish+tha tish+tha ya hum hum swa ha /
NG0756:174: lha min dmag dpung g.yul bzlog cing *//
NG0756:175: lha dmag dkar po'i dbugs 'byin pas //
NG0756:178: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0756:179: na ma dz+nya na ma ha ka la ya /
NG0756:180: na ma:karma bya maha ka la ya /
NG0756:181: na mo ma tri rda ki ni na ga na ya /
NG0756:182: de nas rnal 'byor rgyud bzhin mchod pas mchod //
NG0756:183: bstod pas tshigs bcad dbyangs dang bcas pas brjod //
NG0756:184: de rjes gsang sngags dag par bzlas par bya //
NG0756:185: om maha ka la trag shar /
NG0756:186: ma ha ka la sa ho yam du dza /
NG0756:187: gtso bo'i bsnyen sngags yi ge bcu drug pa'o //
NG0756:188: bka' bstod sngags kyang rtsa sngags de nyid do //
NG0756:189: om badzra yak+sha prah+ma hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:190: yi ge bcu pa dbyangs can ma'i sngags so //
NG0756:191: om badzra yak+sha shri ma ha ka li hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:192: yi ge bcu gsum pa nag mo'i sngags so //
NG0756:193: om badzra yak+sha pa ta li hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:194: srin mo mgo 'phyang ma'i sngags so //
NG0756:195: om badzra kam ka ri kam ka ri hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:196: yi ge bcu gnyis pa rdo rje pho nya mo gtso mo'i sngags so //
NG0756:197: om badzra ro ru ru tsa la a shu+u ga me hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:198: yi ge bco lnga pa 'phags ma nag gru chen mo'i sngags so //
NG0756:199: om badzra re ma ti hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:200: yi ge dgu pa bdag nyid chen mo'i sngags so //
NG0756:201: om badzra he he he hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0756:202: yi ge dgu pa rdo rje dga' mo'i sngags so //
NG0756:203: om kling bam byin no snying la ya /
NG0756:205: ma ha ka la hum hum phat phat /
NG0756:206: yi ge nyer gcig 'khor gyi sngags so //
NG0756:207: ma ni shag trag a ni rak+sha sha tse tse srog rbud /
NG0756:208: om ma ra ya shig ma trig rak+sha sha ma ra ya phye /
NG0756:209: ma ni rak+sha sha ma ra ya phye /
NG0756:211: a mu kam dzi pa ta rbad /
NG0756:212: rak+sha shi ni sha ku ru thum thum rbad rbad rbud /
NG0756:214: srog la rbad thibs rbad myos /
NG0756:215: srog la thun rbad b+h+yo ya /
NG0756:216: yi ge bdun bcu don dgu pa gsad pa'i drag sngags so //
NG0756:217: om tsit+ta tsit+ta ni ra ni ra ma sha ma tang ka ru sha /
NG0756:218: yi ge bco lnga pa dgug pa'i sngags so //
NG0756:219: che ge mo am ku sha dza dza /
NG0756:220: yi ge brgyad pa dgug pa'i sngags so //
NG0756:222: om lam hum lam ma ha ka la che ge mo stam b+ha ya nan /
NG0756:223: yi ge bco lnga pa mnan pa'i sngags so //
NG0756:224: bi sha dza ra pi kham du lang bi sha dza ra pi kham du lang ha sod ya /
NG0756:225: yi ge bcu gcig pa ltas ngan dbab pa'i sngags so //
NG0756:226: om dz+nya na ma ha ka la sa pa ri wa re /
NG0756:227: i dam ba lin+ta gr-i h+na gr-i h+na kha kha kha hi pu dza swa ha /
NG0756:228: yi ge sum cu gcig pa gtor ma'i sngags so //
NG0756:229: de dag las dang po gtso dang bka' bstod kyi bsnyen sngags bzlas /
NG0756:230: thun mthar mchod gtor gtor ma bsngo //
NG0756:231: smon lam gdab cing bskul tshig @#//
NG0756:234: de ltar 'grug pa'i rtags ma byung bar du bsnyen pa bya ste /
NG0756:235: gal te mi 'grub pa'am ldog pa'i rtags byung na /
NG0756:236: man ngag ldan pa gang dgos 'byor byas la /
NG0756:238: bsgrub pa la nan tan bskyed /
NG0756:239: de la ldog pa'i rtags ni /
NG0756:240: sdom dang sdigs bu rmi ba dang *//
NG0756:241: gcan gzan rang la rmugs pa dang *//
NG0756:242: mi la sogs pa'i sems can 'khrug pa dang *//
NG0756:244: sngags pa rang la brdeg pa dang */
NG0756:247: mi sdug pa ston pa dang */
NG0756:250: mi gtsang ba'i 'dam rdzab la sogs pa rmi ba 'byung *//
NG0756:253: dre'u khyim du byung ba dang */
NG0756:254: zhon pa la sogs pa lug khyu rmi ba la sogs mi 'grub pa'o //
NG0756:255: 'grub pa'i rtags ni slob dpon dang */
NG0756:257: btsad po dang btsun pa dang */
NG0756:259: yul gyi gtso bo la sogs pa'i mi chen po mang du rmi ba dang */
NG0756:260: chos pa gang dag rang la chos smra ba dang */
NG0756:261: legs nyes kyi gros smra ba dang */
NG0756:262: bden brdzun ji ltar 'ong ba'i snga ltas ston pa dang */
NG0756:263: gzhan yang mchod khang dang */  gdan khri bzang po dang */
NG0756:270: dril bu la sogs pa sgra dang ldan pa dang */
NG0756:271: thod pa bzang po la sogs pa'i phyag mtshan dang */
NG0756:272: bya nag dang khyi nag rmi ba mang du 'byung */
NG0756:273: grub pa'i rtags ni sngags par rang nyid grong khyer gyi dpon du gyur pa dang */
NG0756:274: dmag dpon du gyur pa dang */
NG0756:276: rang gi g.yog byed pa dang */
NG0756:277: gter chen po rnyed pa dang phrad pa dang */
NG0756:279: dar nag gi gur phub pa rmi ba dang */
NG0756:280: dngos su yang khang sgra 'khrog cing gdung sgra 'tsheg 'od 'byung thug chem gyi sgra 'byung */
NG0756:284: dngos su lha'i mtshan ma byas pa rnyed pa dang */
NG0756:285: mkha' 'gro dang mkha' 'gro ma'i sku mthong ba dang */
NG0756:287: lhag par lha'i sku mthong ba dang */
NG0756:291: byin che zhing ting nge 'dzin gsal ba rnams 'byung ngo *//
NG0756:293: ye shes kyi nag po chen po 'grub na /
NG0756:294: las kyi nag po chen po dang */
NG0756:295: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams shugs la 'grub bo //
NG0756:296: de bas na bdag gis 'khor rnams kyi sgrub pa po'i bran dang g.yog tu gyur te /
NG0756:297: ci bsgo ba'i las byed do //
NG0756:298: dgos pa thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NG0756:299: yongs su brten pa bstan pa'o //
NG0756:301: / de nas khro rgyal gshin rje gshed pos dpal
NG0756:302: nag po chen po bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi rgyud 'di
NG0756:303: gsungs pa / drag po'i las la sogs pa gang sgrub par @#//
NG0756:304: 'dod pa gang shis pa'i gnas su sa sngon po
NG0756:305: 'am nag po las dkyil 'khor pang du khru gang
NG0756:307: mda' gang gru bzhi byas la ba'i lci ba chu
NG0756:308: dang bcas pas byug dur sol dang dug khrag sbyar
NG0756:309: bas dbus su gru gsum nag pos byug de'i phyi
NG0756:310: ru re ga zlum pos lan gnyis bskor /
NG0756:311: bar du zla gam gsum 'byung po dang khrag gis dmar por bya /
NG0756:312: zlum po dkar po la mi mgo smug po nag
NG0756:313: po sngon po gsum spel ba'i 'phreng ba dang rtsang
NG0756:314: gis bskor / gru chad ljang khu /
NG0756:317: phyi'i rtsig pa lnga rim du bya /
NG0756:318: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi lha mo'i snam bu dmar po /
NG0756:320: dra ba dang dra phyed dkar pos bya /
NG0756:321: lta bas kha dog sna tshogs par bya /
NG0756:322: sgrub pa'i yo byad rnams phun sum tshogs par byas la bsgrub pa nyams su blang par bya'o //
NG0756:324: tsan dan la sogs pa bsogs te /
NG0756:325: shing tsher ma can gyi mda' la khra dang 'ug pa'i sgro btags la gzugs /
NG0756:328: gri snying mda' la gdags shing rtar gzung ngo *//
NG0756:329: gzungs ston las la gnyer gtad cing dmar thag chad pa'i dus su ting nge 'dzin bstar la /
NG0756:330: om badzra yak+sha de ba ma ha shri hum dza /
NG0756:331: om badzra yak+sha ye ta li hum dza /
NG0756:332: om sarba dza la ku lo hum dza /
NG0756:333: om kam ka kam ka ro ro hum dza /
NG0756:335: de nas gzhan yang mnan pa dang */
NG0756:337: zor gyi las byas te myur du bsgral bar bya'o //
NG0756:338: bstan pa la gnod pa rnams myur du bsgral ba'i ched du /
NG0756:339: bcom ldan 'das kyis dam pa'i chos gsang sngags kyi
NG0756:340: snod dang ldan pa las dang po pa rnams kyi
NG0756:341: don ched du / dpal nag po chen po rje
NG0756:342: mgon po sgrub pa'i thabs rgyud kyi rgyal po mchog
NG0756:343: don ched du / 'di gsungs te / che'o skyes
NG0756:344: bu chen po sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung bar
NG0756:345: 'dod pas dam pa chos skyong kun gyi gtso bo
NG0756:347: 'di ltar dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba khyad par can blangs te /
NG0756:348: byang chub dam par sems bskyed pa byas nas /
NG0756:349: dam tshig dbang bskur thob par byas la rgyud rnams thos bsam byas te /
NG0756:350: sgrub pa nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NG0756:351: de nas dpal nag po chen pos phyi'i rten gos nag dang */
NG0756:356: ye shes lha'i sku gzugs dang */
NG0756:358: nang gi rten dpal nag po chen po'i sku gzugs dang */
NG0756:359: phyag mtshan dang dkyil 'khor bris pa dang */
NG0756:360: nang gi dam tshig gi rdzas rnams bsham /
NG0756:361: gsang ba'i rten skyes pa grir shi ba'i snying ngam /
NG0756:362: de ma rnyed na g.yag gam /
NG0756:368: tshang bar ma rnyed na gang rnyed kyi snying dang */
NG0756:369: de dag gang rnyed pa'i gsob @#//
NG0756:372: bshos bu ri rab gzugs rnams bsham par bya'o //
NG0756:373: gnas gang shis pa dben pa bzang por dkyil 'khor legs par byas la /
NG0756:374: mchod rdzas dang rten rdzas ci 'byor pa bshams la /
NG0756:375: sngags pas stan bde ba la 'dug ste /
NG0756:376: bla ma dkon mchog la skyabs su 'gro ba dang */
NG0756:377: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa gnyis kyi tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i rjes su /
